{"tid":1938052,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎下，拍緊既簡直係贏家","createTime":"2020-03-22T09:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T11:33:26.000Z","uid":249170,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bb674f9e54daf93e933e11a7ce78db40ed3a04b4","tid":1938052,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T09:44:46.000Z","msg":"係呢個時勢<br />\n要盡量避免社交聚會，放左工都要盡快返屋企<br />\n放假又未必出街，怕浪費一個口罩<br />\n今年可以話係全民毒撚年<br />\n<br />\n依個時勢仲周圍去玩的人類簡直非常勇猛<br />\n簡直係用生命去社交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要唔怕自己染病野埋身邊既人<br />\n<br />\n有另一半真係要好好珍惜對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戴住口罩在街浪漫放閃<br />\n仲可以在家享用對方肉體<br />\n<br />\n衰d講句，依家毒撚連雞都冇得叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個時勢拍緊拖有另一半既簡直人生贏家"},{"pid":"7884c434e059a5903565407b3c559f548c4dfa2a","tid":1938052,"uid":209532,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T09:45:32.000Z","msg":"我昨日分手，講呢d？"},{"pid":"5ddabdbf8c73771508921d80bab71037460b240f","tid":1938052,"uid":62841,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7884c434e059a5903565407b3c559f548c4dfa2a","tid":1938052,"uid":209532,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T09:45:32.000Z","msg":"我昨日分手，講呢d？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T09:47:05.000Z","msg":"關我閪事"},{"pid":"decb4d9668ab980ed9f815a4f7b1ae1bbb6c7000","tid":1938052,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7884c434e059a5903565407b3c559f548c4dfa2a","tid":1938052,"uid":209532,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T09:45:32.000Z","msg":"我昨日分手，講呢d？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T11:33:26.000Z","msg":"No"}]}